# Normalize to LF in the repository and check out LF everywhere. Without
# this, a tool or editor that rewrites the tree to CRLF shows up as every
# file being modified (core.autocrlf is false), and a stray `git add -A`
# commits the churn and destroys `git blame`. The `binary` rules below
# still win for the fixtures they match.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary fixtures — never line-ending-convert.
*.pdf binary
*.step binary
*.wrl binary
*.png binary
